## ğŸ” LÆ¯U Ã QUAN TRá»ŒNG

### 1. Skills matching:
- Exact match = 1.0
- Similar = 0.8  
- Unrelated = 0.0

### 2. Years scoring:
- KHÃ”NG chia tá»· lá»‡ Ä‘Æ¡n giáº£n
- DÃ¹ng má»©c Ä‘á»™ (20/18/14/proportional)

### 3. Education:
