- DÃ¹ng so sÃ¡nh level (15/10/5/0)

### 4. Partial matching:
- Responsibilities cÃ³ thá»ƒ 0.4-1.0 (khÃ´ng chá»‰ 0 hoáº·c 1)
- Cá»™ng dá»“n cÃ¡c partial matches

### 5. Stop words:
- Bá»: "and", "the", "for", "with", "a", "an", "in", "on", "at", "to", "of", "from", "by"
- Chá»‰ Ä‘áº¿m tá»« > 3 kÃ½ tá»±

